{{Infobox person | name = Jody Margolin Hahn | image = | image_size = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | othername = Jody Margolin | birth_date = <!--{{Birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}}--> | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | alma_mater = | occupation = Television director | years_active = 1986–present | spouse = | website = }}
'''Jody Margolin Hahn''' is American television director. Her credits include ''[[Malcolm & Eddie]]'', ''[[Hannah Montana]]'', ''[[The Return of Jezebel James]]'', ''[[Rita Rocks]]'', ''[[Wizards of Waverly Place]]'', ''[[Lab Rats (U.S. TV series)|Lab Rats]]'' and ''[[See Dad Run]]''.<ref>[http://www.locatetv.com/person/jody-margolin-hahn/238048#credits Jody Margolin Hahn - Movies and TV], LocateTV</ref> Prior to television directing, she worked as an associate director, production associate and technical coordinator on the sitcoms ''[[Gimme a Break!]]'', ''[[Roseanne (TV series)|Roseanne]]'', ''[[The Nanny]]'' and ''[[Accidentally on Purpose (TV series)|Accidentally on Purpose]]''.
