ardian.com/global/2014/nov/20/mike-nichols|title=Mike Nichols obituary|first=Ronald|last=Bergan|date=20 November 2014|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017|via=The Guardian}}</ref> |1970 |- |''[[Civilization (film)|Civilization]]'' <ref>{{cite news|title= LARGE AUDIENCE IS THRILLED BY INGE SPECTACLE|publisher= Fairbanks Daily Times|date=1916-09-15}}</ref> |1916 |- |''[[Come and See]]'' <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-come-and-see-1985|title=Come and See|publisher=Roger Ebert.com|accessdate=21 September 2017}}</ref> |1985 |- |''[[Coming Home (1978 film)|Coming Home]]'' <ref name="bfi.org.uk">{{cite web|url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/lists/10-great-vietnam-war-films|title=10 great Vietnam war films|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017}}</ref> |1978 |- |''[[Wooden Crosses|Les Croix de bois]]'' <ref name="books.google.be"/> |1932 |- |''[[The Deer Hunter]]'' <ref name="raindance.org"/> |1978 |- |''[[Don't Cry, It's Only Thunder]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.airpower.maxwell.af.mil/airchronicles/aureview/1983/Jan-Feb/suid.html|title=Hollywood and Vietnam|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.be/books?id=ucQeBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA465&lpg=PA465&dq=don't%20cry%20its%20only%20thunder%20anti-war%20film#v=onepage&q=don't%20cry%20its%20only%20thunder%20anti-war%20film|title=Guts and Glory: The Making of the American Military Image in Film|first=Lawrence H.|last=Suid|date=13 January 2015|publisher=University Press of Kentucky|accessdate=14 January 2017|via=Google Books}}</ref> |1982 |- |''[[Dr. Strangelove]]'' <ref name="warchild.ca"/> |1964 |- |''[[Enemies of the People (film)|Enemies of the People]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.internationalfilmcircuit.com/enemies/|title=International Film Circuit, Inc. - distributor of fine films|first=|last=www.riverlightspictures.com/design|publisher=|accessdate=14 January 2017}}</ref> |2009 |- |''[[The Enemy Below]]'' <ref>{{cite web|url=ht